
Mac OSX 10.9 Mavericks:
-----------------------
Here is what a Mac user needs to install to compile a basic OpenGL 
program using the modified Makefile-mac:

- XQuartz

From MacPorts:

- freeglut
- glew


Ubuntu Linux 14.04:
-------------------
Here is what a Linux user needs to install to compile a basic OpenGL 
program using the modified Makefile-linux:

- libglut3-dev
- libglew-dev


To make:
--------

make square


NOTE:
-----
If your system does not support OpenGL 4.2 you might have to change the line
	glutInitContextVersion(4, 2);
to an earlier version, such as
	glutInitContextVersion(2, 1);

